Package: engager
Type: Package
Title: Engager: Analyze Student Engagement from Zoom and Other WebVTT Transcripts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Conor",
                  family = "Healy",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "conorhealy@berkeley.edu")
Description: Takes Zoom and other WebVTT transcripts and student rosters,
    converts them for analysis, and
    analyzes the results for student engagement, with a particular focus on participation equity.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Language: en-US
